header.name: Eternal Lair of Uadjit
header.author: BSP-Dungeon-Generator
header.description: Uadjit is long dead, but people are still afraid to come close to the lair. Now it is controlled by a band of gnolls. Word is that a legendary rod Arhogath is hidden here.

game_elements.name: Item 1
game_elements.description: A half-eaten body of a gnoll, a bat-shaped key close to it.

game_elements.name: Item 2
game_elements.description: A notable stone double door with a keyhole to the north.

game_elements.name: Item 3
game_elements.description: A noble, sleeping in a corner.

game_elements.name: Item 4
game_elements.description: A wand of illusions locked in a magical safe.

game_elements.name: Item 5
game_elements.description: A statue of a rhino, bursts into flames when touched.
